{"tid":8610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以色列擴大F-35機隊　維持區內軍事優勢","createTime":"2016-11-28T12:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T06:40:51.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50703eec21ff0eb1f4e17ddbf8fd8a91dab86cea","tid":8610,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:09:14.000Z","msg":"以色列表示，將擴大該國的新世代F-35戰機機隊，官員相信此舉可以維持國家對中東鄰國的質量上軍事優勢。 <br />\n<br />\n總理內塔尼亞胡辦公室周日宣布，安全內閣批准購買額外17架F-35戰機，將令這種隱形戰機總數增至50架。 <br />\n<br />\nF-35戰機是美國國防部最昂貴的武器計劃，估計耗資近4000億美元。以色列是預定獲得這種戰機的少數盟國之一，第1批戰機預料會於3周左右到達。 <br />\n<br />\n軍方官員相信，這種飛機將令空軍保持對區內敵人的空中優勢，有能力避過最先進雷達系統偵測。"},{"pid":"fcda657170ff026d6274e80bfa62701879ff8a50","tid":8610,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9f5d7c113a38b6458dabcf5ba0fe37ad819b90","tid":8610,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1a327613abf5e403f78b16a7dbcefca9a7ff08","tid":8610,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:34:01.000Z","msg":"六合狂徒係咪未過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd2dc56879acc3b75b3b199869dbcebb7d7ffc9","tid":8610,"uid":37118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2adbf2f24c6645683ac27c6e50f24b335ded25","tid":8610,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:35:50.000Z","msg":"又賣技術比大陸"},{"pid":"5e0566b82e5e9f35b7aebfaafdc9a3e8022da107","tid":8610,"uid":30001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:40:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>六合狂徒係咪未過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />